## 🎯 SINGLE PURPOSE DESCRIPTION (Required)

**Single Purpose:**
```
YouNow Koi Addons provides automation and moderation tools specifically for YouNow broadcasters, including auto-chest collection, chat bot functionality, moderation features, and Discord integration.
```

